INT. HORADRIC VAULT â€“ STUDY ROOM

DONAN and the PLAYER walk through the door. NEYRELLE sits cross legged on the floor, curled over a large tome. 
Scrolls, candles, and other implements of her study ring the area around her. She is deeply absorbed.
The HORADRIC STAFF lies on the floor beside her. The PLAQUE that usually bears it hangs EMPTY on the wall.
Donan is a bit flabbergasted.

Neyrelle startles as he and the Player approach. 
She scrambles to her feet, tossing the book aside and grabbing up the staff. She holds it out in a combat stance.
The Player takes a step forwards, ready to intervene if the conflict escalates. Neyrelle looks to them warily.
Neyrelle lowers her weapon but does not release it.
Neyrelle huffs, putting a hand on her hip.
Neyrelle holds her proud pose, unflinching. Donan shakes his head, dismissing the absurdity of the thought.
